<Project>
  <!--
    Sub-plan 01 Task 8 — pre-existing warnings inventory.

    Partial cleanup shipped 2026-05-02 (T-IGH-01-WARN-CLEANUP):
      - CS9113 (3 sites)   → fixed; removed from suppression list
      - CS9124 (2 sites)   → fixed; removed from suppression list
      - xUnit2009 (1 site) → fixed; removed from suppression list

    Remaining (still suppressed, tracked under WARN-CLEANUP pending task):
      - CS8602 (21 sites) — domain-test `result.Value.X` derefs and 3
        endpoint sites. Needs a Result<T>.Value nullability rework
        (e.g. `[MemberNotNullWhen(true, nameof(Value))]` on a new
        `IsSuccess` overload + tests gain a leading `Assert.True(
        result.IsSuccess)`), not a per-site `!` operator dump.
      - CS0618 (20 sites) — `User.AddMembership(...)` and
        `PlannedActivity.Create(...)` deprecated calls in *Seeder.cs.
        Migration path: switch to FarmMembership + CreateFromTemplate /
        CreateLocallyAdded. Touches production seed code; deserves its
        own PR with seed regression tests.

    With this list, new warnings of OTHER codes still fail under
    /warnaserror; the listed codes remain as warnings (visible in build
    output but not blocking).
  -->
  <PropertyGroup>
    <WarningsNotAsErrors>
      $(WarningsNotAsErrors);
      CS0618;
      CS8602
    </WarningsNotAsErrors>
  </PropertyGroup>
</Project>
